data.description: Welcome Home! This amazing end Townhouse is located in the Westbrook Park area.  It is adorned with an extra large fenced in yard with a concrete patio and firepit area, just perfect for barbeques and family gatherings. As you enter the house to the left is a nice size bow window bringing in plenty of natural lighting which flows evenly through from the living room to the dining room.  The kitchen has a gas range, dishwasher, large window overlooking yard with large counter for cooking. The hardwood floors flow throughout the house.  Upstairs contains two nicely sized bedrooms and one large bedroom along with a full bathroom. Nice size basement with laundry room, door to garage and outside keypad entrance.  There is three off-street parking in back.  Located near all major highways and transportation.   Make your appointment today!
